Installing from sources

   1. Install libidn (apt-get install libidn11-dev)
   2. Unpack idna source package
   3. Go to idna folder and type "phpize && ./configure && make && make install"
   4. Make sure you have extension=idna.so in your php.ini

Compiling IDNA into PHP

   1. Install libidn (apt-get install libidn11-dev)
   2. Unpack idna source package to $PHP_SOURCE_DIR/ext/idna
   3. In php source root directory run commands: "rm configure && ./buildconf --force"
   4. Configure PHP with command "./configure --with-idna"
   5. Run make && make install
